    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Nike India",
    "description": "Grow your career with Nike India! We are hiring a SEO Specialist for our Allahabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Nike India:\nNike India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Referral bonus program\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nike India!",
